videos.description: Remy Martin finds De'Quon Lake under the basket and Lake slams it in for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: ASU's Lake hammers one-handed dunk

videos.description: Tres Tinkle finds Drew Eubanks who throws down a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Oregon State's Eubanks slams home posterizing dunk

videos.description: Arizona State's Tra Holder falls down and turns the ball over, leading to Oregon State's Ronnie Stacy scoring a transition layup. Holder would later check back into the game.
videos.headline: Holder turns over ball after apparent injury

videos.description: Tres Tinkle chucks the ball across the court to Stephen Thompson Jr. who lays it in.
videos.headline: Beavers' Thompson with an easy layup

videos.description: The Sun Devils' De'Quon Lake denies an Oregon State layup, then Shannon Evans passes it to Mickey Mitchell who throws down the hammer.
videos.headline: ASU with a steal and slam

videos.description: Stephen Thompson Jr. makes back-to-back three-pointers from the wing.
videos.headline: Oregon State's Thompson drains back-to-back 3s

videos.description: Drew Eubanks drives in for the lay-in and knocks down ASU's Vitaliy Mitchell.
videos.headline: Beavers' Eubanks with an up-and-under layup

videos.description: Shannon Evans threads the ball to Kimani Lawrence under the basket, who then slams it in for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Sun Devils' Lawrence hammers it home

videos.description: De'Quon Lake jumps up for a rebound dunk, but the ball bounces off the iron.
videos.headline: ASU's Lake missses dunk
